The salient features of the new species include the following: frons brown, except broad transversal stripe between ocelli and narrow stripe at apex yellowish white, along near apex of median carina with several short transversal stripes, yellowish white (
Fig. 3E
); genae with 2–3 light brown spots (
Fig. 3E
); antennal segment I subsagittate, markedly flattened, with median longitudinal carina, the ventral apical angle longer than dorsal apical angle (
Fig. 4B
); ventral margin of pygofer with 3 medioventral processes short, median one slightly longer than lateral ones (
Fig. 4D
); genital styles swollen subapically (
Fig. 4H
).

